thread.title: Whistleblower says Canadian company worked on software to find Republican voters

title: Whistleblower says Canadian company worked on software to find Republican voters
text:
Whistleblower says Canadian company worked on software to find Republican voters 7:24pm IST - 01:11 
Cambridge Analytica whistleblower Christopher Wylie says Canadian company AggregateIQ worked on a software used to identify Republican voters ahead of the 2016 U.S. election. Rough cut (no reporter narration).
